{{#if user.name}}
<div id="project_state_header" style="color: white;">
    <ul class="nav nav-pills">
        <li id="pill_creation"><a href="#">Creation</a></li>
        <li id="pill_incubation"><a href="#" >Incubation</a></li>
        <li id="pill_campagne"><a href="#" >Campagne</a></li>
        <li id="pill_fin"><a href="#" >Fin</a></li>
    </ul>
</div>
<div id="project_header" class="row-fluid control-group">
    <h3 id="project_title" class="span6">
        {{#if name}}
            <strong class="project_attr" id="project_title">{{name}}</strong>
        {{else}}
            <input id="project_title_input" class="project_attr_input" type="text" placeholder="Titre du projet" style="display: none;" value=""/>
            <strong class="project_attr" id="project_title">Titre du projet</strong>   
        {{/if}}
        <small>, par <a href="#" id="project_author">{{user.name}}</a></small>
    </h3>
    <h3 class="span6 text-right">
        <small class="text-info project_attr">
            0 jour restant
            <a href="#" id="tp_toolTip">
                &nbsp;<i class="icon-time"></i>
            </a>
        </small>
        {{#if deadline}}
        {{else}}
            <div data-date-format="dd-mm-yyyy" data-date="" id="datePicker" class="input-append date project_attr_input" style="display: none;">
                <input type="text" readonly="" value="" size="16" >
                <span class="add-on"><i class="icon-calendar"></i></span>
            </div>
        {{/if}}

    </h3>
</div>
<div id="project_body" class="row-fluid">
    <div class="bs-docs-example">
        <ul class="nav nav-tabs">
            <li class="" id="tab_home"><a data-toggle="tab" href="#home"><i class="icon-list-alt"></i> Accueil</a></li>
            <li class="" id="tab_members"><a id="members_pill_link" data-toggle="tab" href="#news"><i class="icon-envelope"></i> Membres</a></li>
            <li class="" id="tab_comments"><a data-toggle="tab" href="#comments"><i class="icon-comment"></i> Commentaires</a></li>
        </ul>
        <div class="tab-content">
            <div id="home" class="tab-pane fade active in">
                <div class="row-fluid" id="project_content">
                    <div class="span8">
                        <div class="row-fluid">
                            <div class="span12">
                                {{#if thumbnails}}
                                    {{#each thumbnails}}
                                        <a class="thumbnail" href="#" ><img id="project_thumbnail" alt="ALT NAME" src="{{this}}"></a>
                                    {{/each}}
                                {{else}}
                                    <a class="thumbnail" href="#" ><img id="project_thumbnail" alt="ALT NAME" src="http://placehold.it/650x250"></a>
                                {{/if}}
                                <input type="file" id="project_thumbnail_input" style="display: none;"/>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="horizontal_divider row-fluid">&nbsp;</div>
                        <div class="row-fluid">
                            <div class="span12">
                                <p><strong>Description :</strong></p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="row-fluid">
                            <div class="span12 well">
                                <textarea id="project_description_input" class="project_attr_input span12" rows="10" style="display: none;" >
                                    {{#if description}}
                                        {{description}}
                                    {{else}}
                                        Description de votre projet
                                    {{/if}}
                                </textarea>
                                <p id="project_description" class="project_attr" style="cursor: pointer">
                                    {{#if description}}
                                        {{description}}
                                    {{else}}
                                        Description de votre projet
                                    {{/if}}
                                </p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="span4" >
                        <p class="text-center"><strong>Topics & Tags</strong></p>
                        <div class="row-fluid">
                            <div class="span11 text-center">
                                <form id="formSearchTags" class="navbar-form form-search">
                                    <input type="text" style="margin-bottom: auto; margin-top: auto;" autocomplete="off" placeholder="Search projects" class="search-query typeahead input-medium span10" id="inputSearchTags">
                                    <input type="submit" style="display: none;" value="search">
                                </form>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="row-fluid">
                            <div class="span11" id="tag_list">
                                {{#each tags}}
                                    <a href='/col/projects_by_tag/{{this}}'><span class='label label-info'>{{this}}</span></a> , 
                                {{/each}}
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div id="news" class="tab-pane fade">
                <h4>Liste des membres participants aux projets :</h4>
                <p>Pas de membre participant au projet pour l'instant</p>
                <h4>Envoyer une invitation à un utilisateur KickStartUtt :</h4>
                    <div class="<div class="row-fluid">
                        <div class="span4" id="members_list"></div>
                        <div class="span4"><ul id="membersProject"></ul></div>
                    </div>
                    
            </div>
            <div id="comments" class="tab-pane fade">
                <p>Etsy mixtape wayfarers, ethical wes anderson tofu before they sold out mcsweeney's organic lomo retro fanny pack lo-fi farm-to-table readymade. Messenger bag gentrify pitchfork tattooed craft beer, iphone skateboard locavore carles etsy salvia banksy hoodie helvetica. DIY synth PBR banksy irony. Leggings gentrify squid 8-bit cred pitchfork. Williamsburg banh mi whatever gluten-free, carles pitchfork biodiesel fixie etsy retro mlkshk vice blog. Scenester cred you probably haven't heard of them, vinyl craft beer blog stumptown. Pitchfork sustainable tofu synth chambray yr.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
      </div>
<!--    -->
</div>

<div id="project_footer" class="row-fluid text-center">
    <a id="project_validator" class="btn btn-success btn-large" href="#validateInfo" data-toggle="modal">Valider</a>
</div>

<!-- Modal -->
<div id="validateInfo" class="modal hide fade" tabindex="-1" role="dialog" aria-labelledby="myModalLabel" aria-hidden="true">
    <div class="modal-header">
        <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal" aria-hidden="true">×</button>
        <h3 id="myModalLabel">Validation des informations</h3>
    </div>
    <div class="modal-body">
    </div>
    <div class="modal-footer">
        <button class="btn" data-dismiss="modal" aria-hidden="true">Close</button>
        <button class="btn btn-primary" id="save_change_button">Save changes</button>
    </div>
</div>
{{else}}
<div class="span4 offset4">
    <legend>Please Sign In</legend>
    <div class="alert alert-error" id="alertLogin" style="display: none;">
        <a href="#" data-dismiss="alert" class="close">×</a>Incorrect Username or Password!
    </div>
    <form accept-charset="UTF-8" action="#" method="POST" id="form_signin">
        <input type="text" placeholder="Username" name="username" class="span12" id="username">
        <input type="password" placeholder="Password" name="password" class="span12" id="password">
        <button class="btn btn-info btn-block" name="submit" type="submit">Sign in</button>
    </form>    
</div>
{{/if}}
